        "title": "Dirtyfrag: Universal Linux LPE",
        "href": "https://www.openwall.com/lists/oss-security/2026/05/07/8",
        "score": "625 pts · 256c"
      }
    },
    "text-4a": {
      "type": "Text",
      "props": {
        "text": "Why it matters: Embargo-broken LPE via xfrm-ESP page-cache write + rxrpc. Same sink as Copy Fail; bypasses the algif_aead mitigation; no distro patches.",
        "variant": "body"
      }
    },
    "text-4b": {
      "type": "Text",
      "props": {
        "text": "HN take: \"No patches exist for any distribution. Mitigation: blacklist esp4/esp6/rxrpc in /etc/modprobe.d, rmmod the modules, drop_caches; reboot if exploited.\" — john_strinlai",
        "variant": "caption"
      }
    },
